<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">niht becʒalt künn werden </del> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l10"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein ſchulde noch <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> richten vnd becʒalen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_94_r1l11">vnd Jn darümb vnklaghaft <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
